This app is known as "iBanker", available for iOS (iPhone and iPad).  iBanker replaces paper money in board games like Monopoly® and The Game of Life®! Avoid the hassle of counting cash - keep the paper money in the box and use iBanker instead! With features to send money to and from “the bank”, as well as directly from one player to another, iBanker completely replaces paper money and the job of “banker” in board games.

Add and manage players with the user-friendly iOS interface, including a photo for each player. All of the information is saved when you leave the app, enabling easy breaks in the gameplay, and an Activity Log keeps track of every transaction. Sound effects give each transaction satisfying feedback (and can be turned off in Settings). Change the “Mode” in Settings to automatically set the starting bank account balance and salary to match any of the most popular games - the classic $1500 game is the default. When you are ready to start a new game, “Reset Players” in Settings to reset all players back to the starting bank account value.

The Spinner feature provides the Spin to Win® function for the electronic banking version of The Game of Life®.  It is automatically enabled for the $400K Mode.

